items.content:
# ===================================================================

###*
* An enumeration of easing types.
*
* @module gs
* @class EasingTypes
* @memberof gs
* @constructor
* @static
* @final
###  
class EasingTypes
    @initialize: ->
        ###*
        * @property EASE_IN
        * @type number
        * @static
        * @final
        ###
        @EASE_IN = 1
        ###*
        * @property EASE_OUT
        * @type number
        * @static
        * @final
        ###
        @EASE_OUT = 0
        ###*
        * @property EASE_IN_OUT
        * @type number
        * @static
        * @final
        ###
        @EASE_IN_OUT = 2
        ###*
        * @property EASE_LINEAR
        * @type number
        * @static
        * @final
        ###
        @EASE_LINEAR = 0
        ###*
        * @property EASE_QUADRATIC
        * @type number
        * @static
        * @final
        ###
        @EASE_QUADRATIC = 1
        ###*
        * @property EASE_CUBIC
        * @type number
        * @static
        * @final
        ###
        @EASE_CUBIC = 2
        ###*
        * @property EASE_QUARTIC
        * @type number
        * @static
        * @final
        ###
        @EASE_QUARTIC = 3
        ###*
        * @property EASE_QUINTIC
        * @type number
        * @static
        * @final
        ###
        @EASE_QUINTIC = 4
        ###*
        * @property EASE_SINUSOIDAL
        * @type number
        * @static
        * @final
        ###
        @EASE_SINUSOIDAL = 5
        ###*
        * @property EASE_EXPONENTIAL
        * @type number
        * @static
        * @final
        ###
        @EASE_EXPONENTIAL = 6
        ###*
        * @property EASE_CIRCULAR
        * @type number
        * @static
        * @final
        ###
        @EASE_CIRCULAR = 7
        ###*
        * @property EASE_ELASTIC
        * @type number
        * @static
        * @final
        ###
        @EASE_ELASTIC = 8
        ###*
        * @property EASE_BOUNCE
        * @type number
        * @static
        * @final
        ###
        @EASE_BOUNCE = 9
        ###*
        * @property EASE_BACK
        * @type number
        * @static
        * @final
        ###
        @EASE_BACK = 10
    
EasingTypes.initialize()
gs.EasingTypes = EasingTypes
